high_descs: Walk forward then turn left and walk up to the oven.
Take the potato out of the microwave above the oven and then close the microwave door.
Walk over to the fridge that is behind you.
Put the potato in the fridge and after a couple seconds take it out and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the oven and look up at the microwave.
Put the chilled sweet potato in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Take one step then turn left and walk to the stove, then look up.
Open the microwave and take the potato out of the microwave and close the door.
Look down then turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the potato inside for three seconds, then open the fridge and take the potato.
Turn around and take one step, then turn to the right and walk to the stove.
Look up and put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cool the potato to be cooked.

high_descs: Move forward then turn left at the fridge; look up.
Open the microwave, take the potato from inside, then close it.
Turn around, go to the wall, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the potato inside of the fridge.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to return to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the potato inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the microwave.
